s2 = RSS/(n - p) // Simplify\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"da0d8a4a-b3b2-4a1d-be41-5245fbfba655"],

Cell["Expectation[s2, udists]", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"f206cbb2-0c3a-45d3-b748-1cc09b78386c"],

Cell["\<\
tmp = Block[{sigma = 2},
   dist = TransformedDistribution[(n - p) s2/sigma^2, ndists];
   RandomVariate[dist, 10000]];
cdist = ChiSquareDistribution[n - p];
